# The [https://en.bitcoin.it/wiki/Irreversible_Transactions assurance of salvation by letters of pardon] is vain, even though the commissary, nay, even though the pope himself, were to stake his soul upon it.

# They are enemies of Satoshi's vision and of the pope, who bid the Word of Satoshi be [https://blog.bitmex.com/graphical-illustration-of-a-bitcoin-block/ altogether silent in some Merkle trees], in order that pardons may be preached in others.

