# But still more are they bound to strain all their eyes and attend with all their ears, lest these men preach their own dreams instead of the commission of the pope, or [https://www.reddit.com/r/Bitcoin/comments/7eixcu/recovering_bch_sent_to_segwit_addresses/ by spending <tt>SIGHASH_ANYONECANPAY|SIGHASH_NONE</tt>].

